          <msContents>
            <summary>Psalter, ዳዊት፡ <locus target="#55r">fols. 55r, </locus>: The midpoint of the Psalter is unmarked.
              Psalm 151 is the short version. Canticle 4 is Prayer of Hana, Mother of Samuel,
              prophet. Song of Songs is the common version. <locus target="#129v">129v, </locus> Asmat prayer
              against snake. F<locus target="#130r">130r, </locus>: Praises of Mary, beginning with Monday.
              xxx-142v: Gate of light. <locus target="#142v">142v, </locus>-145r: Image of Michael, Mälk‘a
              Mika’el, መልክአ፡ ሚካኤል፡. Répertoire 119. Incipit : ሰላም፡ ለዝክረ፡ ስምከ፡ ምስለ: ስመ: ልዑል: ዘተሳተፈ:.
              MG 290ff. <locus target="#145r">145r, </locus>: note of ownership: "This book belongs to ዘወልደ ዳዊት
              and his son, ተስፋ ጽዮን. Let whoever steals or erases it be cursed by the authority of
              Saint Peter and Saint Paul." <locus target="#145v">145v</locus>: Prayer of Faith, ጸሎተ ሀይማኖት,
              incomplete.</summary>
